9 An Act relating to game and fish; amending 29 O.S.
2021, Section 4-114, as amended by Section 6, Chapter
10 6, O.S.L. 2024 (29 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 4-114),
which relates to lifetime fishing and combination
11 hunting and fishing licenses; creating lifetime
nonresident fishing and combination hunting and
12 fishing licenses; establishing requirements for
license; providing license fee; providing an
13 effective date; and declaring an emergency.
14
15
